QuestData.Title: Teegan's Troubles
QuestData.Description: The Admiral will be pleased that Northwatch is almost secured, but if we're to keep a grip on this continent we're going to need to maintain the supply lines to the interior.$B$BJust before the assault I received the strangest of reports from Corporal Teegan, who's in charge of maintaining our contact with Forward Command. Says he's having trouble with the "jungle?" There's no jungle in the Barrens!$B$BFollow the upper road out of Northwatch and see if you can render any assistance to our wayward Corporal.
QuestData.LogDescription: Report to Corporal Teegan at Teegan's Expedition in Southern Barrens.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Report to Corporal Teegan at Teegan's Expedition in Southern Barrens.
QuestData.RewardText: So, Paxton says there's no jungle in the Barrens? What do you call THIS!?$B$BI've got a pile of supplies to move to the interior and my camp has been overrun by a forest that - I swear - grows by the hour!
